{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.360", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.080", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.760", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.520", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es ist richtig: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.880", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Verdienstunterschied zwischen M\u00e4nnern und Frauen in Deutschland ist hoch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.240", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zu hoch\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.520", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "egal ob wir \u00fcber die 21\u00a0Prozent vom Equal Pay Day oder \u00fcber 6\u00a0Prozent sprechen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.960", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Warum soll ich als Frau bei gleicher Qualifikation und Leistung im gleichen Job weniger verdienen als meine m\u00e4nnlichen Kollegen? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.280", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist unfair, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.680", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und daran m\u00fcssen wir arbeiten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.560", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.920", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Unsere Antwort darauf darf aber eben nicht sein: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.080", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mehr Staat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.280", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mehr B\u00fcrokratie und absurde Strafen f\u00fcr die Unternehmen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.600", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb lehnen wir die Antr\u00e4ge zum Entgeltgleichheitsgesetz und zum Verbandsklagerecht ab."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "70.920", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie sind eine Zumutung und setzen sich null mit den Ursachen auseinander."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "70.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.720", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Viel wichtiger ist es doch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.560", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den Frauen die Chance zu geben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "78.320", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "am Berufsleben voll teilzuhaben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "78.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.760", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben gut ausgebildete Frauen in unserem Land. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.840", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Doch sobald Kinder da sind oder Angeh\u00f6rige gepflegt werden m\u00fcssen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.120", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist die Vollzeitstelle oft pass\u00e9, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.480", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und es droht eine komplette berufliche Pause. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.280", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das gilt es zu \u00e4ndern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.040", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was wir dazu brauchen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "98.600", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist mehr Flexibilit\u00e4t, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "98.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "100.200", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "eine Flexibilit\u00e4t, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "100.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.880", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die es uns erleichtert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "103.720", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "im Beruf zu bleiben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "103.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.880", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vollzeit arbeiten zu k\u00f6nnen und nicht Teilzeit arbeiten zu m\u00fcssen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.480", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Neue Arbeitszeitmodelle wie das, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "122.160", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das wir gestern in unserem Antrag zur \u00c4nderung des Arbeitszeitgesetzes angeregt haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "122.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "124.240", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "f\u00fchren zu mehr Flexibilit\u00e4t. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "124.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "130.000", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Digitalisierung er\u00f6ffnet uns mit Homeoffice und mobilem Arbeiten mehr Freiraum: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "130.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "131.120", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "f\u00fcr die Pflege, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "131.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.400", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "f\u00fcr die Betreuung oder f\u00fcr die Weiterbildung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "137.480", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "So kommt der Staat seiner Aufgabe nach, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "137.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.680", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Voraussetzungen zu schaffen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "142.080", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht mehr und nicht weniger."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "142.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "144.720", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das sind die Voraussetzungen daf\u00fcr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "144.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.480", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass M\u00e4nner und Frauen selbstbestimmt entscheiden k\u00f6nnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "157.040", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie sie famili\u00e4res und berufliches Leben partnerschaftlich angehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "157.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "161.200", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ohne dass einer benachteiligt wird."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "161.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.840", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Au\u00dferdem sollten wir Frauen noch st\u00e4rker ermutigen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "168.480", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "klassische M\u00e4nnerbranchen zu erobern: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "168.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "169.600", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "MINT-F\u00e4cher, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "169.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.120", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jobs, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "172.240", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die eben besser bezahlt werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "172.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.200", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gleichzeitig sollten wir aber auch daf\u00fcr sorgen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.440", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass mehr M\u00e4nner vermeintliche Frauenberufe ergreifen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "180.920", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gestatten Sie eine Zwischenfrage, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "180.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.640", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Kollegin?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "182.080", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "182.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "186.000", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Kollege soll jetzt erst einmal zuh\u00f6ren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "186.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "186.640", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich wei\u00df, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "186.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "190.640", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass das Ver\u00e4nderungen f\u00fcr unsere Gesellschaft bedeutet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "190.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "193.800", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber genau diese Ver\u00e4nderung w\u00fcrde uns guttun; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "193.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.600", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn die Menschen in den sozialen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.000", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "erzieherischen und pflegerischen Berufen tragen gro\u00dfe Verantwortung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "204.560", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie brauchen mehr Wertsch\u00e4tzung und auch eine bessere Verg\u00fctung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "204.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.840", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "So schlie\u00dfen wir n\u00e4mlich endlich die Lohnl\u00fccke zwischen den verschiedenen Geschlechtern."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "212.880", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber es muss uns auch gelingen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "212.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.520", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mehr Frauen in F\u00fchrungspositionen zu holen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "219.040", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn Frauen in leitenden Positionen sind erfolgreich."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "219.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "221.320", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u2013\u00a0Da brauchen Sie nicht zu lachen.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "221.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "226.400", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gemischte Teams sind nachweislich produktiver; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "226.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "230.160", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das ist doch im Interesse eines jeden Arbeitgebers. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "230.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.760", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir als FDP appellieren daher an die Unternehmer, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "241.560", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ihrer Verantwortung durch faire und leistungsorientierte Bezahlung unabh\u00e4ngig vom Geschlecht nachzukommen;"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "241.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "247.440", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn das w\u00e4re eine soziale Innovation; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "247.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.400", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das w\u00e4re endlich einmal wirkliche Gleichberechtigung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "255.600", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir Frauen d\u00fcrfen uns nicht mit weniger zufriedengeben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "255.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "259.640", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir m\u00fcssen selbstbewusst auftreten und verhandeln. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "259.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "263.600", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir m\u00fcssen zusammenhalten und uns gegenseitig st\u00e4rken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "263.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "267.840", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und wir d\u00fcrfen diese Unterst\u00fctzung auch von den M\u00e4nnern erwarten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "267.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "270.720", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daf\u00fcr sollten wir uns einsetzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "270.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "272.000", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "272.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "276.440", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herzlichen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "276.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "279.960", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Wort hat die Kollegin Ulle Schauws von B\u00fcndnis\u00a090/Die Gr\u00fcnen."
   ]
  }
